    "body": "To create a log file in parallel all you need to do is add file appender to example log4j config provided at : https://besu.hyperledger.org/en/stable/HowTo/Monitor/Logging/\r\nTo the above add an appender:\r\n\r\n<File name=\"FILEOUT\" fileName=\"your_log_filename.log\" append=\"false\">\r\n      <PatternLayout>\r\n        <Pattern>%d{yyyyMMdd HH:mm:ss} %-5p [%t] %C{2} %F%L - %m%n</Pattern>\r\n      </PatternLayout>\r\n</File>\r\n\r\n",
